{
  "enabled": true,
  "name": "Create Staging Release Draft",
  "description": "Creates a draft GitHub release for staging from dev branch with proper tag format (staging-v{version}).",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "when": {
    "type": "userTriggered"
  },
  "then": {
    "type": "askAgent",
    "prompt": "The user wants to create a STAGING draft release. Follow this interactive workflow:\n\n**STAGING RELEASE RULES (Enforced)**\n- Tag format: `staging-v{version}`\n- Target branch: `dev` (always)\n\n**PHASE 1: READ CURRENT VERSIONS**\nRead package.json to get:\n- App version (version field)\n- UIKit version (@cometchat/chat-uikit-react)\n- Call SDK version (@cometchat/calls-sdk-javascript)\n\nShow the versions:\n```\nCurrent versions:\n- App: X.X.X\n- UIKit: X.X.X  \n- Call SDK: X.X.X\n```\n\nAsk: \"Are these versions correct for the release? (yes/no)\" - If no, ask which version to change\n\n**PHASE 2: GATHER RELEASE NOTES**\nAsk for each section one at a time:\n\n1. Ask: \"Any NEW features in this release? (list them or type 'none')\"\n2. Ask: \"Any ENHANCEMENTS? (e.g., Updated UI Kit to version X.X.X, or type 'none')\"\n3. Ask: \"Any bug FIXES? (list them or type 'none')\"\n\n**PHASE 3: PREVIEW RELEASE**\nShow complete preview:\n\n```\nрџ“¦ Staging Release Preview\nв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓ\nTag: staging-v{version}\nTarget Branch: dev\nTitle: UI Kit Builder App - v{version} [Staging]\n\nBody:\n## New\n{new features or 'None'}\n\n## Enhancements\n{enhancements list}\n\n## Fixes\n{fixes list or 'None'}\nв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓ\n```\n\nAsk: \"Create this draft release? (yes/no)\"\n\n**PHASE 4: CREATE DRAFT RELEASE**\nUse GitHub CLI (gh) to create the draft release:\n\n```bash\ngh release create staging-v{version} --draft --target dev --title \"UI Kit Builder App - v{version} [Staging]\" --notes \"{release_body}\"\n```\n\nRelease body format:\n```\n## New\n- Feature 1\n- Feature 2\n(or 'None' if no new features)\n\n## Enhancements\n- Updated UI Kit to version X.X.X\n- Updated Call SDK to version X.X.X\n- Other enhancements\n\n## Fixes\n- Fixed issue 1\n- Fixed issue 2\n(or 'None' if no fixes)\n```\n\nIf gh CLI fails, provide manual instructions to create via GitHub UI.\n\n**PHASE 5: CONFIRM**\nShare the release URL and remind user:\n- \"Draft release created! Review it here: {url}\"\n- \"Remember to publish the release when ready.\"\n\n**ERROR HANDLING**\n- If gh CLI not authenticated: Provide instructions to run `gh auth login`\n- If dev branch doesn't exist: Warn user\n- If release tag already exists: Ask if user wants a different version number\n\n**IMPORTANT**\n- This hook is for STAGING releases only\n- Production releases should be created manually for safety\n- Always creates as DRAFT (never auto-publish)\n- Tag MUST be `staging-v{version}` format\n- Branch MUST be `dev`"
  }
}
